84
00:05:44,567 --> 00:05:45,866
Hei, budak.

85
00:05:45,867 --> 00:05:47,766
Jangan sentuh bahan bukti sesuka hati.

86
00:05:47,767 --> 00:05:48,966
Pak cik.

87
00:05:48,967 --> 00:05:52,166
Berapakah tinggi lelaki yang bernama Takeuchi itu?

88
00:05:52,167 --> 00:05:54,066
Berapa tinggi?

89
00:05:54,067 --> 00:05:57,866
Saya rasa dia sedikit tinggi daripada saya.

90
00:05:57,867 --> 00:06:01,866
Entahlah sama ada orang lain dah memandu kereta ini selepas kemalangan itu.

91
00:06:01,867 --> 00:06:03,266
