124
00:07:37,167 --> 00:07:38,566
Oh, begitu.

125
00:07:38,567 --> 00:07:40,666
Encik?

126
00:07:40,667 --> 00:07:42,666
Adakah pemandu itu

127
00:07:42,667 --> 00:07:44,966
