180
00:10:14,067 --> 00:10:15,166
Cik Kuriyama.

181
00:10:15,167 --> 00:10:16,366
Ya.

182
00:10:16,367 --> 00:10:17,766
Bolehkah kamu hubungi syarikat penyiasatan

183
